<% provide(:title, 'Training Programs') %>

<div class="container mainContainer">
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8 col-lg-8 col-md-offset-2 col-lg-offset-2 padding-10-px">
			<p class="lead">Next Level Distance Running offers two packages for you to chose 
				from- the Online Training Program and the Face to Face Program.  Whether
				you're new to running or an accomplished runner looking to take the next step, 
				you'll be sure to find the best assistance from Ronnie Carda at Next Level 
				Distance Running.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-10-px col-md-offset-3 col-lg-offset-3">
			<%= image_tag("runner_jogging_morning.jpg", :class=> "img-circle") %>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row-fluid">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-10-px">
			<h4 class="lead text-center">Online Training Program</h4>

			<p>The Online Training Package is an excellent choice for runners seeking to reach 
				the next level on their own.  This package offers great videos and power points 
				that help you learn about preparing yourself for any event.  You will 
				communicate with the trainer at least once every other week.
			</p>

			<p >With the online program you will receive:</p>
			
			<ul>
				<li>Personalized training program designed to meet your individual needs</li>
				<li>Bi-monthly training log check-in</li>
				 <li>Ongoing training adjustments to your training program</li>
				 <li>Online power point information which covers various topics such as:</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Running form</li>
				            	<li>Nutrition</li>
				         	<li>Injury prevention and treatment</li>
				           	<li>Program design</li>
				            	<li>Event preparation</li>
				            	<li>Event strategy</li>
						<li class="price">Season Cost: $200.00</li>
					</ul>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-10-px">
			<h4 class="lead text-center">Face to Face Training Program</h4>
			
			<p>This is the best training package to optimize your effort with your trainer and to 
				stay on course with your training plan.  In addition to all of the benefits of the 
				online package, the Face to Face Training Program also includes the following 
				program benefits:
			</p>
			<ul>
			        <li>Ask the trainer access</li>
				<li>Running form analysis</li>
				<li>Weekly group workouts</li>
				<ul>
					<li>includes warm-up activities, various workout types, cool down 
						and stretching activities, core training activities and strength 
						training ideas
					</li>
				</ul> 
						
				 <li class="price">Season Cost: $300.00</li>
			</ul>	
		</div>
		
	</div>

	<div class="row-fluid">	
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-10-px">
			<h4 class="lead text-center">Workout Types</h4>
			<p>Group workouts will be individualized according to pace and volume and will 
				include:
			</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Group distance runs</li>
					<li>Tempo Runs</li>
					<li>Hill workouts</li>
					<li>Interval Workouts</li>
				</ul>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 padding-10-px">
			<h4 class="lead text-center">Payment</h4>
			<p>Payments can be made by check, money order or through PayPal.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

	



    